text: Winn-Dixie is a supermarket chain. They have stores in Georgia, Louisiana, Mississippi, Alabama and Florida. The company once served Oklahoma, Texas, South Carolina, North Carolina and New Mexico. Now, they mainly serve the Southeastern United States. The company is headquartered in Jacksonville, Florida. Winn-Dixie has its private label Chek for sodas. The sodas have over 20 different flavors. Winn-Dixie was established in 1925. It is owned by Southeastern Grocers.
